Har bir jon - nimani taqdim qildiyu \nnimani ta'xir qildi - biladir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,70]}]}

{"text":"6. Ey Inson! Seni nima Karamli Robbing \nhaqida g`ururga ketkazdi?!","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,66]}]}

{"text":"7. U seni to`la-to`kis va mo'tadil qilib yaratgandi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,52]}]}

{"text":"17. Va, jazo kuni nima ekanini senga nima bildirdi?","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,51]}]}

{"text":"18. So`ng, jazo kuni nima ekanini \nsenga nima bildirdi?","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,55]}]}

{"text":"19. O`sha kunda hech bir jon boshqa bir jon uchun biror narsa qilish imkoniga molik emas. \nU kunda barcha ish Allohning O`ziga xos.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,131]}]}
